Lynx buys Quadra for initial 2 . 66 mln stg . Lynx Holdings Plc said on Wednesday it has bought Quadra Computer Services Ltd for an initial payment of 2 . 66 million stg in cash and shares . An additional consideration of up to 665 , 000 stg is payable by Lynx if profit before tax at the computer software company for the year to 31 January 1997 is greater than or equal to 700 , 000 stg . Quadra had turnover of 3 , 40 million stg and pretax profit of 392 , 000 stg for the year ended 31 January 1996 . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 4019 
